    {
      "id": "ex_f2_1_3",
      "title": "垂直線",
      "question": "求與直線 $y = 2x - 1$ 垂直且過原點的直線方程式。",
      "answer": "$y = -\\frac{1}{2}x$",
      "solution": "垂直線斜率：$m_1 \\cdot m_2 = -1$\n\n$2 \\cdot m_2 = -1$ → $m_2 = -\\frac{1}{2}$\n\n過原點：$y = -\\frac{1}{2}x$",
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "type": "calc",
