    {
      "id": "ex_f2_2_1",
      "title": "二次函數頂點",
      "question": "求 $f(x) = x^2 - 4x + 3$ 的頂點坐標。",
      "answer": "$(2, -1)$",
      "solution": "方法一：配方法\n$f(x) = x^2 - 4x + 3$\n$= (x^2 - 4x + 4) - 4 + 3$\n$= (x-2)^2 - 1$\n頂點：$(2, -1)$\n\n方法二：公式\n$h = -\\frac{b}{2a} = -\\frac{-4}{2} = 2$\n$k = f(2) = 4 - 8 + 3 = -1$",
      "difficulty": "easy",
      "type": "calc",
      "relatedNodes": ["f2.2"],
      "tags": ["二次函數", "頂點"]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex_f2_2_2",
      "title": "對稱軸",
